data.description: Wonderful family home on large corner lot.  The upstairs bedrooms have been combined for a HUGE primary bedroom with private 3/4 bath en suite.  Newer flooring in primary bathroom.  The crown molding is a nice touch in this oversized bedroom that comes with dual closets.  The living room which can also function as a dining room has plenty of space for a large table and chairs.  The kitchen is light and bright and will include all of the appliances (gas stove range too!)   The cabinets are upgraded and the granite is a nice upgrade as well.   The lower level has a large family room with French doors.  The two lower level bedrooms are a great size and the 3/4 bath is attached to one of the bedrooms.  The lower level has a dedicated laundry room and the washer and dryer are included.  The Lennox furnace is both electric and a gas heat pump.  The water heater is Rheem.  The windows are newer and the glass front door new. Large deck off of kitchen makes the perfect place to entertain friends and family. The exterior of the home is a maintenance free vinyl siding.  The large corner lot would be a great asset for someone wanting to have street access for extra storage.  The shed is included, and the sellers just poured an extra large patio for entertaining.
